<h2>@내용</h2>
<h3>- ESG 기업</h3>
<pre>
## 3. COMPANY INTRODUCTION: ECO-FRIENDLY ESG SHEET
- **Placement:** Append a dedicated "Eco-Friendly ESG Management" sheet within the 'Company Profile (회사소개)' section.
- **Design Philosophy:** Clean, sustainable, professional corporate identity. Use a refined green and slate-gray accent palette.
- **Content Structure:**
  - **Title:** Sustainable Water Technology (친환경 ESG 경영)
  - **Subtitle:** "Leading the future of eco-friendly water systems with high-efficiency, zero-emission engineering."
</pre>

<h3>- 제품</h3>
<pre>
### PART 2: Product & Technology Page - Production Pump Lineup (Revised)
- Keep the current high-end card grid layout. Replace all default pump descriptions and image assets with the authorized 11-pump lineup from the 'BAtech_pump_product_summary' documentation.
- Visual Assets Direction: Each pump card must depict a premium, hyper-realistic 3D industrial render of the specific pump type, placed on a clean, minimal, non-distracting studio white background.

* Card 1: 다단벌류트펌프 (Multistage Volute Pump)
  - Description: 고압 이송에 적합하며, 여러 단의 임펠러를 장착하여 안정적인 압력과 유동 제어를 지원합니다. (Suitable for high-pressure transfer, generating stable system pressure through multiple impeller stages.)
  - Visual: High-pressure multistage horizontal volute pump with segmented casing.
</pre>

<h3>- 실적</h3>
<pre>
## 5. REINFORCED BUSINESS PORTFOLIO & TRACK RECORD SHEET
- **Placement:** Update the existing "Business Track Record (주요 사업 실적)" section.
- **Design Philosophy:** Keep the current minimalist and organized structure, but expand the content density to reflect deep industrial expertise.
- **Structured Project Records:**
  - **Water Infrastructure Engineering (상하수도 및 공공 설비):**
    - Municipal Water Treatment Plant Pump Installation & Optimization (Chuncheon-si Waterworks Office)
    - Regional Sewage Treatment Facility Pumping System Turnkey Construction
    - Deep Well Groundwater Development Projects (Agricultural Infrastructure Corporation)
  - **Industrial Facility & Equipment Supply (산업체 및 생산 설비):**
    - High-Pressure Boiler Feed Pump Installation for Regional Cogeneration Plants
    - Corrosion-Resistant Chemical/Sludge Pump System Integration for Major Chemical Plants
    - Emergency Firefighting Pumping Systems & Pressure Maintenance Stations
  - **Maintenance & Reconstruction (유지보수 및 긴급 수리 실적):**
    - Comprehensive Overhaul & Calibration of Large-scale Municipal Double Suction Pumps
    - Variable Frequency Drive (VFD) Booster System Retrofitting for Energy Efficiency Upgrades
    - 24/7 Rapid Emergency Response Repair Records for Regional Waterway Infrastructures
</pre>

