<h2>@그 외</h2>
<h3>- BGM</h3>
<pre>
## 1. AUDIO ENGINE & BGM CONTROLLER (MUTE BUG FIX)
- **Current Issue:** BGM volume only decreases incrementally but fails to trigger complete mute (0.0 volume).
- **Update Instruction:** 
  - Refactor the custom HTML5 Audio node or background music state manager. 
  - Ensure the "Mute" toggle button sets `audio.muted = true` and explicitly sets `audio.volume = 0`.
  - Provide a clear icon state change on the UI: Dynamic Soundwave Icon (when active) ⭢ Muted/Slash Speaker Icon (when muted).
  - Implement smooth transition handling: transition volume exponentially to 0 over 150ms to prevent clipping artifacts, then apply hard mute state.
</pre>

